{"word":"μειαγωγέω","slug":"μειαγωγέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n65686\" key=\"meiagwge/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μειᾰγωγ-έω</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">μεῖον</etym>) <sense id=\"n65686.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bring the sacrificial lamb to the scale</tr_>, hence metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μ. τὴν τραγῳδίαν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">weigh</tr_> it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">as you would a lamb</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg009.perseus-grc1:798\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ra.\">Ra.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">798</biblScope> </bibl>:— hence <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μειᾰγωγ-εῖον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, and <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μειᾰγωγ-ία</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author> </bibl>:</sense> </entryFree>"}]}